01:46.773 --> 01:48.366
-(fingers snap)
-(jukebox stops playing)

01:50.811 --> 01:52.210
That's terrific, Fonz.

01:52.346 --> 01:53.541
Thanks.

01:53.680 --> 01:55.444
Uh... Rich.

01:55.582 --> 01:56.447
Rich!

01:56.583 --> 01:57.846
CHACHI:
He's not here.

01:57.985 --> 01:59.419
Not here, Fonz.

01:59.553 --> 02:02.113
Uh-huh, yeah, your place,
an emergency.

02:02.255 --> 02:03.984
Will do, Fonz, yeah.

02:04.124 --> 02:06.593
Oh, hey, Fonz,
turn it on again, will you?

02:08.127 --> 02:09.994
-(snaps fingers)
-(jukebox playing music)

02:12.633 --> 02:13.498
Terrific.

02:13.634 --> 02:14.624
Thanks, Fonz.

